summary: Here is a female Dunmer for your face-preset needs!
descriptionHtml:
[size=4][b]This file is a Nexus exclusive. If it is found anywhere, including Bethesda.net (as I do have an account there), and is not uploaded by me, it is stolen. Please report any stolen mods you see. :)[/b][/size]


[img]http://i989.photobucket.com/albums/af11/selenameeka/72850_screenshots_20161018220921_1.jpg[/img]


[size=3]This mod is free for you to use as a template or to use as your own character's face. If you like her, please endorse, maybe comment, and enjoy!

Mods used in the screenshots:
Hair: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?]ApachiiSky Hair [/url]
Warpaint: Vanilla (Retexture by [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/67147/?]Painterly[/url])
Skin: [url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/seren4xx/15342092530]SRG Skin[/url] - you can also use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG skin[/url]. Looks good, too. I use SRG's more muscle variant.
Eyes: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]
Eyebrows: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30411/?]Brows[/url]
Body: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?]UNP[/url] (just my preference, she'll work with any body).
Freckles: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/52841/?]Freckle Mania[/url]
Uses [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/24273/?]Ethereal Elven Overhaul[/url]


Installation:
Requires Racemenu and SKSE!
1. Open your Data folder in Skyrim
2. Download this file
3. Open Hathor and copy all the files from the data folder to your Skyrim's data folder[/size]
author: selenameeka
